            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Deanae <supplied reason="lost">Lu</supplied>cif<supplied reason="lost">erae</supplied> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Stellius <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinti</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> V</supplied><expan><abbr>ol</abbr><ex>tinia</ex></expan> Vopiscus <lb n="3"/>testamento fieri iussit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): In Z. 1 gibt es Reste von dem zweiten E in Deanae und von dem F in Luciferae. In Z. 2 ist das T in Stellius noch erkennbar.</p>
            </div>
